      "bgName": "01-3d",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_05-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "…………お姉ちゃんと、話そうと思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve decided to talk to my sister.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_05-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "……いいのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you sure about it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_05-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "はい。でも、{user}さんも\n芽衣もいなくて大丈夫です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. But I don’t need you there‚ {user}‚\nand I don’t need Mei there either.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.826145100593564,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_05-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃんが何を話しているか\n聞く必要はないので",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whatever my sister says to me‚\nI don’t need to hear it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.19281176726023,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_05-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "えっ？　でも、それじゃ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? But if you do that‚ then…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.892811767260229,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_05-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "それでいいんです。だから二人きりにして下さい\n今度は盗み聞きはなしで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m okay with that. So please leave me alone with her.\nDon’t eavesdrop this time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.992811767260235,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_05-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "分かった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay then.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.42614510059357,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 27.3628117673
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 27.3628117673
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_shed-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 27.62614510059358
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_05-mna001.m4a",
      "text": "……あ……おかえり……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh. Hi…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.42614510059357,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 34.24947865009308
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_05-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "って言っても、そんなの分からないか……\n大丈夫か？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I guess you wouldn’t know that.\nAre you alright?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.24947865009308,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_05-mna002.m4a",
      "text": "そ。何度も同じこと聞かないよーに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. Stop asking the same thing over and over.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.71614531675974,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 44.73226794401804
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_05-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "……琴乃が話したいと言っている",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono says she wants to talk to you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.73226794401804,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_05-mna003.m4a",
      "text": "えっ？　本当に？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Really?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.2682770649592,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 50.21827716032663
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_05-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "一方的に喋りたいだけだって……それでもいいか？\nああ。でも、麻奈の声は聞こえなくていいと言ってる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She’d rather the conversation be one-sided. Are you still okay with it?\nYes. But she says she doesn’t want to hear what you have to say.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.21827716032663,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 60.21827716032663
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_05-mna004.m4a",
      "text": "うん……琴乃がそうしたいなら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. As long as that’s what Kotono wants.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.21827716032663,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_05-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃、中に入ってきてくれ\n……分かった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono. You can come in now.\n…Okay.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.83741544882455,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6266.666666666659,
          "startTime": 70.10408211549121
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5433.333333333344,
          "startTime": 69.2707487821579
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 69.2707487821579
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_05-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "俺は寮のリビングで待っているから\n終わったら来てくれ。……それじゃ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ll be waiting for you in the living room at the dorm.\nCome see me when you’re done. Bye.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.7707487821579,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5300.000000000011,
          "startTime": 77.7707487821579
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-close-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4400.0000000000055,
          "startTime": 79.1707487821579
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 79.6707487821579
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_05-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My sister…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 83.13333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_05-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "（とてもお姉ちゃんがいるようには思えないな）\n（……でも、ちゃんと言っておこう）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(It doesn’t feel at all like my sister is here.)\n(But I’d better say what I have to say.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.76666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 90.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_05-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "（莉央さん達と話して）\n（せっかく自分の気持ちが分かったんだから）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Because talking with Rio and the others)\n(finally made me realize my true feelings.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.73333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 95.4
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tears-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 96.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_05-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "私ね、お姉ちゃんとずっと話したいと思ってた\n聞きたいこと、謝りたいこと、沢山あったから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Listen‚ I’ve wanted to talk to you all this time.\nThere were things I wanted to ask… things I wanted to apologize for… so many things.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.73333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_05-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃんがどう思ってたのか、今どう思ってるのか\nずっと聞きたいって思ってた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How you felt about everything… how you feel about everything now…\nI always wanted to ask you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 114.866666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_05-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "（何も見えないけど）\n（聞こえていると信じて、私は続ける）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I can’t see anything.)\n(But I trust that she’s listening‚ and I continue.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 120.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_05-ktn011.m4a",
      "text": "でも、何も聞かないことにした\nそれは私が自分で決着付けなきゃいけないことだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I decided not to ask you anything.\nBecause these are all issues I have to resolve on my own.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 129.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_05-ktn012.m4a",
      "text": "（お姉ちゃんが驚いた顔を見せた、ような気がした）\n（何も見えないけど、そんな気がした）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I get the sense that my sister is surprised to hear that.)\n(I can’t see anything‚ but I just get that sense.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 138.93333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_05-ktn013.m4a",
      "text": "私ね、アイドルってなんなのか、どうしてお姉ちゃんが\nあんなに夢中で頑張ってたのか、ずっと分からなかった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Listen‚ I had no idea what an idol was exactly… or why you\nwere so devoted to working so hard at it… I never understood.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_05-ktn014.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃんが事故でいなくなって、自分がアイドルに\nなってからも、実はよく分かってなかったんだと思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even after you died in that accident‚ and after I became an idol‚\nthe truth is‚ I think I still didn’t understand.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.73333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 156.56666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_05-ktn015.m4a",
      "text": "…………でも、今は分かる\nこの仕事がどれだけ魅力的か",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But now I understand.\nI know just how alluring this job is.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 159.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 162.333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_05-ktn016.m4a",
      "text": "ステージに立って、みんなを元気にしたり\n楽しんでもらうことが、どれだけ素敵なことか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I stand on stage… when I make people energized‚\nand happy‚ I know just how wonderful it is that I can do that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.33333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 169
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_05-ktn017.m4a",
      "text": "だから！　だから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So that’s why! That’s why…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 169.63333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 172.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_05-ktn018.m4a",
      "text": "（お姉ちゃんの気配を近くに感じながら）\n（私は一番伝えたいことを口にした）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(As I feel Mana’s presence close to me‚)\n(I tell her the words I’ve wanted to say the most.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 176.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_achieve-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 179.5
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 179.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_05-ktn019.m4a",
      "text": "私は、もうお姉ちゃんの後を追いかけない\nかわりに決勝のステージに立ちたいとも思わない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I won’t chase after you anymore.\nI won’t wish to perform at the Grand Prix finals in your place.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 183.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 186.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_05-ktn020.m4a",
      "text": "もっと沢山の人に楽しんでもらうために\nもっともっとすごいアイドルになるために、頑張る",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Instead‚ I’ll work hard to bring joy to as many people as possible.\nI’ll work hard to become an even better‚ even stronger idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 190.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_05-ktn021.m4a",
      "text": "自分がなりたいアイドルを、自分で見つけて\nそこに向かって歩いて行く",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ll find out what kind of idol I want to become‚\nand that’s the goal I’ll work towards.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 197.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 199.23333333333332
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_05-ktn022.m4a",
      "text": "それが私が決めたこと\nお姉ちゃんに伝えたかったこと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is a decision I’ve made on my own.\nThis is what I’ve wanted to tell you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 203.73333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 206.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_05-ktn023.m4a",
      "text": "嬉しい？　それとも悲しいかな……分からないけど\nでも、きっと聞いてるよね。見てくれてるよね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you happy? Or maybe you’re sad… I don’t know which.\nBut I know you’re listening to me. I know you’re watching over me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 213.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 220.033333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_05-ktn024.m4a",
      "text": "（物音一つしない部屋で）\n（その時、頬に温かい何かを感じた）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(In this deadly quiet room‚)\n(I feel something warm touch my cheek.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 223,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 227.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_05-ktn025.m4a",
      "text": "（誰かの腕に抱き締められているような）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I feel like someone’s hugging me from behind.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 227.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_05-ktn026.m4a",
      "text": "（……私は「それでいいんだよ」と言われている）\n（ような気がした）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(And she’s saying‚ “You made the right decision.”)\n(That’s the feeling I have.)",
        "id": ""
